NK037(ji)011:1: // 'khon lugs rnying ma gur mgon srog gi spu gri'i
NK037(ji)011:2: sgrub thabs dbang bskur dang bcas pa bdud 'joms spu
NK037(ji)011:3: gri zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK037(ji)011:5: bla ma dpal chen he ru kar //
NK037(ji)011:6: yang yang gus pas rab btud nas //
NK037(ji)011:7: gur mgon srog gi spu gri yi //
NK037(ji)011:8: sgrub thabs byin rlabs mdo tsam bshad //
NK037(ji)011:14: gtor chog tsam la phyi nang mchod pas 'thus kyang /
NK037(ji)011:15: bsnyen sgrub bam dbang dang 'brel na /
NK037(ji)011:16: stegs bur man+dala gru bzhi phyi rdo ra me ris
NK037(ji)011:17: bskor ba nang du zlum skor gyi dbus su gru
NK037(ji)011:19: khyams zla gam la dur khrod dang /
NK037(ji)011:20: gru chad bzhi phyogs mdog byas pa'i dbus su phur
NK037(ji)011:21: pa dar nag gi cod pan can phur gdan dang
NK037(ji)011:22: bcas pa bkod / phyogs bzhir b+han+d+ha dam rdzas kyis gang ba dang /
NK037(ji)011:24: dpal gtor zur gsum pa dang /
NK037(ji)011:25: rak+sha'am thod pa'i phreng ba rnams bkod /
NK037(ji)011:27: mdun du sman dang rak+ta bsham /
NK037(ji)011:28: gzhan chu gnyis nyer spyod sogs mchod pa rnams ci bder bkod la /
NK037(ji)011:30: sngon gtor gyis mtshon pa'i mkho ba'i yo byad rnams kyang 'du bya'o //
NK037(ji)011:32: thog mar bdag bskyed rdo rje'i rigs kyi khro bo gang rung gcig sngon du btang bar gsungs pas /
NK037(ji)011:33: yang dag phyag rgya gcig pa'i bsgom bzlas byas na 'brel la /
NK037(ji)011:34: bka' brgyad phyag rgya rkyang sgrub byas kyang chog /
NK037(ji)011:35: gang ltar skyabs sems tshogs bsags nas sgom bzlas bsdu
NK037(ji)011:36: ldangs kyi bar du byas la sngon 'gro dkar gtor
NK037(ji)011:38: rat+na pany+tsa +aahmh'u gis 'dod yon lnga ldan bdud rtsi'i gter du brlab /
NK037(ji)011:39: b+h+au mi pa ti sa pa ri w+aa ra badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs mgron dgug /
NK037(ji)011:41: a k+aa ro sogs btags pa lan gsum gyis gtor ma phul la /
NK037(ji)011:42: sa bdag lha klu 'khor dang bcas //
NK037(ji)011:43: gtor ma phul ba 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)011:44: bdag gi sgrub pa ma thon par //
NK037(ji)011:45: khyed la gnas 'di bdag g.yar gyis //
NK037(ji)011:46: ci bde bar ni gzhan du song //
NK037(ji)011:48: b+h+r+au mi pa ti sa pa ri b+aa ra gats+tshasa gshegs /
NK037(ji)011:52: stong pa'i ngang la h'u las gnas khang dur khrod
NK037(ji)011:53: drag po'i rgyan bkod tshad med pa dang ldan pa'i
NK037(ji)011:54: dbus su / h'u yig nag po dpag tu med
NK037(ji)011:55: pa las byung ba'i phyi nang mchod pa'i dam rdzas
NK037(ji)011:56: mkha' dbyings kun tu rgyas par gang bar gyur /
NK037(ji)011:58: shap+da pany+tsa k+aa ma gu na +aahmh'u /
NK037(ji)011:61: stong pa'i ngang las yam las rlung ram las me
NK037(ji)011:62: kam las mi mgo'i sgyed bu gsum la brten pa'i
NK037(ji)011:63: a yig las byung ba'i thod pa'i snod du bcud
NK037(ji)011:65: m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam las bdud rtsi lnga dang
NK037(ji)011:66: sgron ma lngar gyur pa so so'i sa bon gyis
NK037(ji)011:67: mtshan pa dang bcas pa'i 'og gi rlung g.yos me
NK037(ji)011:68: sbar rdzas thams cad zhu zhing 'dres pa'i steng gi
NK037(ji)011:69: nam mkha' la +aahmh'u gi yi ge gsum gnas pa
NK037(ji)011:70: las 'phros pa'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa
NK037(ji)011:71: thams cad kyi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi bdud
NK037(ji)011:72: rtsi bkug / yi ge gsum la thim ste rim
NK037(ji)011:73: par zhu ba las dam tshig gi rdzas dang ro
NK037(ji)011:74: rtsi bkug / gcig tu gyur / ma h+aa ba
NK037(ji)011:75: lim ta te dzo ba lim ta b+aa la ba
NK037(ji)011:76: te guh+ya sid+d+hi sa ma ya h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK037(ji)011:78: a las byung ba'i thod pa yangs shing rgya che
NK037(ji)011:79: ba gnyis kyi nang du h'u t+r+aam h+r+aihkham las byung
NK037(ji)011:80: ba'i sman bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen po dang /
NK037(ji)011:81: ram las byung ba'i rak+ta dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag gi rgya mtshor gyur /
NK037(ji)011:82: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK037(ji)011:83: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h+r+aith+aa /
NK037(ji)011:84: zhes lan gsum gsum gyis sman raka byin gyis brlab bo //
NK037(ji)011:85: mdun bskyed gong ltar bsang sbyang /
NK037(ji)011:86: stong pa'i ngang las rdo rje'i sa gzhi dang rwa
NK037(ji)011:87: gur me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus su sum las rin
NK037(ji)011:88: po che'i brag ri'i steng du /
NK037(ji)011:89: dur khrod chen po'i klong dkyil du sna tshogs rdo
NK037(ji)011:90: rje'i lte bar e las chos kyi 'byung gnas kyi
NK037(ji)011:91: dbus su / pam pad+ma man+da la h'u las pad+ma /
NK037(ji)011:92: a tsan+d+ra man+da la h'u las zla ba /
NK037(ji)011:93: ma s+aur+ya man+da la h'u las nyi ma /
NK037(ji)011:94: n+ri ljang gu las dgra bo'i bam chen rnams brtsegs pa'i gdan du gyur /
NK037(ji)011:95: de'i steng du h'u mthing nag gi 'od kyi 'phro 'du las /
NK037(ji)011:96: nag po chen po'i skur gyur /
NK037(ji)011:97: ma h+aa k+aa la h'u phata /
NK037(ji)011:98: rdo rje nag po chen po sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK037(ji)011:99: gri gug dang thod khrag thugs kar steng 'og tu 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)011:100: sma ra smin ma dbu skra gyen du bardzesa shing rdo rje'i gshog pa 'bar ba rdeb pa /
NK037(ji)011:105: stag lpags rlon pa'i sham thabs /
NK037(ji)011:106: mi lpags dang glang chen lpags pa'i stod g.yogs gsol ba /
NK037(ji)011:107: zhabs phur bu 'bar ba'i rnam pa can dgra bo'i snying gar gzir ba /
NK037(ji)011:108: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)011:111: rang gi snying ga nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK037(ji)011:112: rang dang mdun bskyed kyi bar du nyi ma'i gdan la gshin rje gshed du gyur pa ni /
NK037(ji)011:113: sku mdog mthing nag be con dang zhags pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK037(ji)011:114: de nyid kyi phyag mtshan lcags kyur gyur te /
NK037(ji)011:115: ye shes pa bkug par mos la /
NK037(ji)011:117: sngon tshe dpal chen spyan snga ru //
NK037(ji)011:118: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK037(ji)011:119: byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas 'di ru //
NK037(ji)011:120: drag po'i las la spyan 'dren gshegs //
NK037(ji)011:121: e h+ye hi sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa l+aa ya /
NK037(ji)011:122: ma h+aa k+aa ru ni k+aa ya /
NK037(ji)011:123: sa m+aa dzah dzah h'u bam hoh dam tshig pa la thim nas gnyis med du gyur /
NK037(ji)011:124: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ye b+h+yah ar+g+ham nas /
NK037(ji)011:126: lcags kyu 'od du zhu ba las bum par gyur te dbang bskur /
NK037(ji)011:127: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK037(ji)011:128: w+aa ka a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)011:132: chu'i lhag ma yar lud pa las /
NK037(ji)011:133: gshin rje gshed nyid dbu rgyan du bzhugs par gyur /
NK037(ji)011:134: phyi nang gi mchod pa rnams rim par phul bar mos la /
NK037(ji)011:135: rdo rje khro rgyal nag po'i sku //
NK037(ji)011:136: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK037(ji)011:137: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK037(ji)011:138: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK037(ji)011:139: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgya lan gsum brjod /
NK037(ji)011:140: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK037(ji)011:141: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK037(ji)011:142: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK037(ji)011:143: 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK037(ji)011:144: +aahmh'u sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)011:145: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK037(ji)011:146: dmar gyi mchod pa rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK037(ji)011:147: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)011:148: ma lus gshegs nas bsnam du gsol //
NK037(ji)011:149: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ru d+hi ra kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)011:150: ma h+aa m+aam sa la kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)011:151: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK037(ji)011:152: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK037(ji)011:153: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab tu brgyan //
NK037(ji)011:154: thugs dam bzhin du ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK037(ji)011:155: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la i dam
NK037(ji)011:156: push+pam d+h+au pam gan+d+ham ba lim ta pra t+aits+tsha hoh
NK037(ji)011:157: grih+na kh+aa hi / badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa la kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)011:159: nang mchod rdo rjes dkrugs shing gtor ma la bran /
NK037(ji)011:162: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub 'thob //
NK037(ji)011:166: rdo rje snying gar gtad la /
NK037(ji)011:168: zung zhig zung zhig rdo rje che //
NK037(ji)011:169: khyod kyis rtag tu 'di zung zhig /
NK037(ji)011:170: gal te bsgo ba ma nyan na //
NK037(ji)011:171: nag po khyod nyid nyams par gyur //
NK037(ji)011:172: ces brjod cing dam la bzhag go //
NK037(ji)011:173: de nas mgon po'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK037(ji)011:174: gyi steng du h'u mthing nag gi mthar sngags kyi
NK037(ji)011:175: phreng bas g.yas su bskor ba /
NK037(ji)011:176: bdag bskyed thugs ka'i 'od zer phog pas thugs kyi
NK037(ji)011:177: rgyud rab tu bskul te ci 'dod pa'i phrin las
NK037(ji)011:178: rab 'byams thogs pa med par bsgrubs par mos la
NK037(ji)011:179: / ma h+aa k+aa la h'u phata /
NK037(ji)011:180: ces bsnyen sngags gtso bor bzla /
NK037(ji)011:181: de wa ma h+aa k+aa la tri yam dzahdzah ma
NK037(ji)011:182: h+aa k+aa la tri yam dgra bo m+aa ra ya
NK037(ji)011:183: / ma h+aa k+aa la tri yam thum ril rbad k+ai la ya sha rbad /
NK037(ji)011:184: dgra bo n+ri m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK037(ji)011:186: sarba big+h+nana na bam h'u phata /
NK037(ji)011:187: ces btags pa'ang cung zad bazla'o //
NK037(ji)011:191: der n+ri dang tri las byung ba'i dgra bgegs shin tu rid pa'i rnam pa can du gyur /
NK037(ji)011:192: ma h+aa k+aa la'i sprul pa'i dmag tshogs mdun du lhags par bsam la /
NK037(ji)011:193: gtor ma kha gsos la gong bzhin phul /
NK037(ji)011:195: khros pa'i gzugs ldan gdug pa gang //
NK037(ji)011:196: ji ltar rgyal bas mi 'dul ba //
NK037(ji)011:197: smon lam sems kyi gzugs can de //
NK037(ji)011:200: ma h+aa k+aa la dgra bgegs gdug pa can m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK037(ji)011:203: srin po'i gzugs kyi gdug pa can //
NK037(ji)011:204: tshar gcod byang chub sems dpa' ste //
NK037(ji)011:205: grong khyer sum brtsegs 'jigs byed pa //
NK037(ji)011:206: gtum po khyod la bdag bstod do //
NK037(ji)011:207: mdog nag gzugs thung gzi brjid che //
NK037(ji)011:208: gdug pa tshar gcod gri gug g.yas //
NK037(ji)011:209: g.yon pa gdug pa'i khrag bkang snod //
NK037(ji)011:210: thod phreng can la bdag bstod do //
NK037(ji)011:211: khros pas zhabs brdabs sa gzhi g.yo //
NK037(ji)011:212: 'jigs pa'i gad mos ri rab bsgyel //
NK037(ji)011:213: dam tshig nyams pa'i snying 'byin pa //
NK037(ji)011:214: dam tshig can la bdag bstod do //
NK037(ji)011:217: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK037(ji)011:218: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK037(ji)011:219: bstan pa bsrung bar thugs bskyed la //
NK037(ji)011:220: nag po khyod ni yin pa ste //
NK037(ji)011:221: gang gis dkon mchog gsum po dang //
NK037(ji)011:222: bla ma brnyas byed sems can 'tshe //
NK037(ji)011:223: bdag la gnod byed dgra dang bgegs //
NK037(ji)011:224: thams cad khyod kyis gzhom pa dang //
NK037(ji)011:225: bstan pa bsrung bar mdzad du gsol //
NK037(ji)011:227: 'bar ma me yi khron pa ru //
NK037(ji)011:228: rab tu bcings nas mgon bral ba'i //
NK037(ji)011:229: gzas po'i spyi bor phur bu che //
NK037(ji)011:230: nag po chen po phyag gnyis pa //
NK037(ji)011:231: gnam lcags 'bar ba zur gsum dpal //
NK037(ji)011:232: rab tu bsnun no mnal ba'i sems //
NK037(ji)011:233: rnam par ma rig bral gyur nas //
NK037(ji)011:234: dpal gyis rjes su 'dzin par shog /
NK037(ji)011:235: gong gi sngags sham bu can de nyid dang /
NK037(ji)011:236: sarba big+h+n+aana mung+ga ra a ko ta ya h'u phata /
NK037(ji)011:242: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)011:245: bdag dang slob mar bcas pa la /
NK037(ji)011:248: bsam pa'i don thams cad 'grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK037(ji)011:250: gtor chog rkyang pa'i skabs 'og nas bshad pa'i rjes chog rnams bya'o //
NK037(ji)011:252: slob dpon gyis kyang 'og gi dbang rnams blang /
NK037(ji)011:253: slob ma la khrus bgegs bskrad srung 'khor sems bskyed gsal gdab sngon du 'gro bas /
NK037(ji)011:255: de'ang mkha' 'gro ma rdo rje gur gyi rgyud le'u bco lnga pa las /
NK037(ji)011:256: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rdo rje nag po chen po'i sgrub thabs 'di /
NK037(ji)011:257: nyid kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK037(ji)011:258: h'u gi yi ge las skyes pa //
NK037(ji)011:259: phyag gnyis pa dang zhal gcig ldan //
NK037(ji)011:260: kha dog gnag cing cher 'bar ba //
NK037(ji)011:261: gri gug thod khrag 'dzin pa po //
NK037(ji)011:262: mgo bo'i phreng bas do shal byas //
NK037(ji)011:263: mche ba chen pos 'jigs par byed //
NK037(ji)011:264: gzugs thung gzi brjid chen po nyid //
NK037(ji)011:266: snying po bcas gsal bar bstan pa dang /
NK037(ji)011:267: rdo rje gdan bzhi'i rgyud rgyas pa las kyang bstan cing /
NK037(ji)011:268: bram ze mchog sred la sogs pa'i grub thob rnams
NK037(ji)011:269: las lo chen rin chen bzang po'i bar du brgyud
NK037(ji)011:270: de / gsar ma'i phyogs su rje btsun sa skya
NK037(ji)011:271: pa la bka' bab pa'i rtsa ba'i mgon po lcam
NK037(ji)011:272: de / dral / mgon po yab rkyang /
NK037(ji)011:275: 'phags pa klu sgrub nas slob dpon klu'i byang chub brgyad pa'i gur yum can /
NK037(ji)011:276: n+aa ro mee tri'i man ngag mnga' bdag mar pa
NK037(ji)011:277: lo ts+aa nas brgyud pa rngog lugs rgyud mgon rnams
NK037(ji)011:278: dang / gzhan yang gri gug lha dgu ma sogs
NK037(ji)011:279: gri gug gi rigs rnams kyang 'di nyid kyi rnam
NK037(ji)011:280: dang / 'gyur yin la / ber nag zangs mgrin
NK037(ji)011:281: can sogs 'di nyid kyi las mgon yin pas rgya
NK037(ji)011:283: 'dir slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+ma
NK037(ji)011:284: ka ras 'khon lo ts+aa ba klu'i dbang po dang
NK037(ji)011:285: / des 'khor rdo rje rin chen la stsal ba
NK037(ji)011:286: nas bzung 'khon ston rig pa 'dzin pa'i gdung rabs
NK037(ji)011:287: bar ma chad pa las byon pa'i snga 'gyur rnying
NK037(ji)011:288: ma bka' ma'i lugs gur mgon srog gi spu gri'am
NK037(ji)011:289: phur zhabs can du grags pa'i byin rlabs dbang bskur
NK037(ji)011:290: gyi rim pa bsgrub pa la sogs kyis mtshams sbyor
NK037(ji)011:292: me tog dang bcas pa'i thal mo sbyar la gsol ba 'debs pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK037(ji)011:293: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK037(ji)011:294: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang //
NK037(ji)011:295: sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK037(ji)011:296: dbang dang dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK037(ji)011:297: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK037(ji)011:298: rgyud rnam par dag par bya ba'i slad du slob
NK037(ji)011:299: dpon dpal he ru kar gsal ba dang mdun bskyed
NK037(ji)011:300: dpal ldan nag po chen po la rgyal ba sras
NK037(ji)011:301: dang bka' sdod bcas pas bskor te bzhugs pa'i drung
NK037(ji)011:302: du / rgyun bshags tshul bzhin bya ba'i blos tshigs
NK037(ji)011:303: rjes su don dran pa'i sgo nas 'di'i rjes zlos
NK037(ji)011:304: du / mdzod / dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK037(ji)011:306: de nas dbang gi gzhi dgod pa'i phyir du sgo
NK037(ji)011:307: gsum sgrims la khyed rang rnams mgon po dam tshig
NK037(ji)011:308: par gsal ba la ye shes bstim zhing dbang bskur
NK037(ji)011:309: rgyas gdab ste bskyed rim yan lag bzhi rdzogs kyis
NK037(ji)011:310: bsgrub dgos pa yin pas bsgom don 'di rnams rim
NK037(ji)011:313: stong pa'i ngang las rdo rje'i sa gzhi gur dang sogs gong bzhin la /
NK037(ji)011:314: de'i steng du khyed rang rnams kyi sems nyid h'u mthing nag gi 'od kyi 'phro 'du las /
NK037(ji)011:315: skad cig gis khyed rang rnams nag po chen po'i
NK037(ji)011:316: skur gyur pa sogs sngar ltar gyis slob ma rnams
NK037(ji)011:317: mgon por bskyed / ye shes pa bkug pa'i skabs
NK037(ji)011:318: su gu gul sogs spos dud dang rol mo'i sgra
NK037(ji)011:319: drag tu byas la gnyis med du bstim zhing mchod
NK037(ji)011:320: mgon por bskyed / / dbang bskur rgyas gdab /
NK037(ji)011:321: dbu rgyan tu bzhugs par gyur par btang la /
NK037(ji)011:322: dbus kyi phur bu dpal nag po chen po'i ye shes phyag rgya'i ngo bos byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK037(ji)011:323: lus kyi sdig sgrib nad gdon byang //
NK037(ji)011:324: lus gzi brjid dang ldan par gyur par mos shig /
NK037(ji)011:325: phur bu spyi bor gtugs shing lag tu gtad la /
NK037(ji)011:326: dpal chen khrag 'thung nag po che //
NK037(ji)011:327: phur bu'i gzugs kyis dgra bo dang //
NK037(ji)011:328: bgegs srog dbang du sdud 'di longs //
NK037(ji)011:329: lha sku sgom pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK037(ji)011:332: des mgon po'i sku'i dbang thob /
NK037(ji)011:333: lha bsgom pa la dbang ba yin pas bskyed pa'i rim pa la brtson par gyis shig /
NK037(ji)011:334: drag po'i phreng ba dpal nag po chen po'i gsung sngags kyi ngo bos byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK037(ji)011:335: ngag gi sdig sgrib nad gdon byang /
NK037(ji)011:336: ngag nus mthu dang ldan par gyur par mos shig /
NK037(ji)011:337: phreng ba mgrin par gtugs shing sbyin la /
NK037(ji)011:338: sgrub pa'i ye shes tshon gang ba //
NK037(ji)011:339: gsang ba'i sngags kyi rab bskyed la //
NK037(ji)011:340: dus dang rgyud du bzla bya ba'i //
NK037(ji)011:341: 'dzab bsnyen phreng ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK037(ji)011:343: w+aa ka a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah des mgon po'i gsung gi dbang thob //
NK037(ji)011:344: sngags bzla ba la dbang ba yin pas bzlas brjod chu bo'i rgyun bzhin du gyis shig /
NK037(ji)011:345: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i gri gug dpal nag po chen
NK037(ji)011:346: po'i thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngo
NK037(ji)011:348: yid kyi sdig sgrib nad gdon byang //
NK037(ji)011:349: sems rtogs pa'i ye shes dang ldan par gyur par mos shig /
NK037(ji)011:350: gri gug snying gar gtugs shing sbyin la /
NK037(ji)011:351: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK037(ji)011:352: bsgral phyir gri gug dbang sbyin pas //
NK037(ji)011:353: bar chad byed pa'i lha dang bdud //
NK037(ji)011:354: sgrol zhing nyon mongs gcod par shog /
NK037(ji)011:357: des mgon po'i thugs kyi dbang thob //
NK037(ji)011:358: ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa la dbang ba yin pas
NK037(ji)011:359: chos nyid 'od gsal gyi rnam 'byor dang ma bral
NK037(ji)011:360: bar gyis shig / thod zhal bdud rtsis bkang ba
NK037(ji)011:361: dpal nag po chen po'i yon tan 'dod 'byung gi
NK037(ji)011:362: ngo bos byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK037(ji)011:363: sgo gsum cha snyoms kyi sdig sgrib nad gdon byang /
NK037(ji)011:364: yon tan rtsol med du rdzogs par gyur par mos shig /
NK037(ji)011:365: b+han+d+ha lte bar bzhag cing gtad la /
NK037(ji)011:366: thod pa byang chub sems kyi rtags //
NK037(ji)011:367: sman mchog ye shes lnga yis gang //
NK037(ji)011:368: yon tan rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK037(ji)011:369: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas thob par shog /
NK037(ji)011:371: gu na a b+hi shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK037(ji)011:372: des mgon po'i yon tan gyi dbang thob //
NK037(ji)011:373: dngos grub sgrub pa la dbang ba yin pas thun
NK037(ji)011:374: mong dang mchog gi sgrub pa la brtson par gyis
NK037(ji)011:375: shig / dpal gyi gtor chen dpal nag po chen
NK037(ji)011:376: po'i phrin las drag po'i ngo bos byin gyis brlabs
NK037(ji)011:377: shig / pas / shes bya dang snyoms 'jug la brten pa'i sdig sgrib nad gdon byang /
NK037(ji)011:378: phrin las thogs med kyi rtsal dang ldan par gyur pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK037(ji)011:379: gtor ma gsang gnas dang lag bar gtad la /
NK037(ji)011:380: gtor ma'i dbang bskur 'di sbyin pas //
NK037(ji)011:381: dgra bgegs bsad cing bskrad pa dang //
NK037(ji)011:382: rmongs shing rengs pa'i phrin las dang //
NK037(ji)011:383: dngos grub 'byung ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK037(ji)011:386: des mgon po'i phrin las kyi dbang thob //
NK037(ji)011:387: las bzhi spyi dang khyad par mngon spyod kyi las
NK037(ji)011:388: sgrub pa la dbang ba yin pas bstan pa bsrung
NK037(ji)011:389: ba'i phrin las la brtson par gyis shig /
NK037(ji)011:390: spro na bla ma brgyud pa'i mtshan nas smos te
NK037(ji)011:391: gtor ma'i bka' bsgo spyi ltar byas kyang rung la
NK037(ji)011:392: 'dir dmigs bsal ma gsungs pas ma byas kyang chog
NK037(ji)011:394: dam tshig bsgrag bzung sogs slob ma'i rjes kyi bya ba rnams spyi dang 'dra /
NK037(ji)011:395: slar yang gtor ma 'bul ba dang /
NK037(ji)011:400: smon lam bkra shis sogs tshang bar bya'o //
NK037(ji)011:402: rig 'dzin kun gyis dga' bas blangs //
NK037(ji)011:403: deng sang ming yang nub tu nye //
NK037(ji)011:404: phan sems kho nas snying por dril //
NK037(ji)011:405: gur mgon phur zhabs can gyi sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK037(ji)011:406: zhes rje btsun thams cad mkhyen pa t+aa ra n+aa
NK037(ji)011:407: tha'i gsung rab las khol du phyungs te kha 'phangs
NK037(ji)011:408: dkyus su bkod cing mtshams sbyor sogs gsal bar byed
NK037(ji)011:409: pa po ni pad+ma gar dbang blo gros mtha' yas
NK037(ji)011:410: te rdzong shod bde gshegs 'dus pa'i sgrub gnas kyi
